rows.label: qev092705_MSG0010
rows.name:
You got the materials already?
You BLADEs are efficient workers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0020
rows.name:
Yeah, these'll be more than enough.
Thanks a lot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0030
rows.name:
That last battle really took a toll on you, didn't it?
Looks like the circuits couldn't bear the heat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0040
rows.name:
Now if I just add this to the cooling system...
it should hold out long enough...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0050
rows.name:
...All right.
Yep, even I should be able to take it from here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0060
rows.name:
Could you give me a sec?
This won't take long.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0070
rows.name: Right. Should be good to go.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0080
rows.name:
It's weird, though.
It really shouldn't have been so unstable...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0090
rows.name:
How did they miss such a glaring defect?
We're days from rollout...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_JNK0100
rows.name: Extol

rows.label: qev092705_SEL0110
rows.name: Sing the Skell's praises.

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0120
rows.name: Yeah, it's a work of art.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0130
rows.name:
I'm glad you find it impressive.
We've wrangled with it for long enough.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_JNK0140
rows.name: Look Doubtful

rows.label: qev092705_SEL0150
rows.name: Ask what was wrong with it.

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0160
rows.name: Wish I knew...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0170
rows.name:
It's a bit hard to ascertain that out here.
I'll need an expert's opinion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0180
rows.name: Though...it's clear the controls are acting up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0190
rows.name:
They're being a little temperamental.
Kinda hard to get to grips with...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0200
rows.name:
The overheating implies it's the steering...
causing an unexpected load on the system...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0210
rows.name: I'll have to mention that to Alicia later.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0220
rows.name:
I'm heading back to NLA.
Would you mind joining me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092705_MSG0230
rows.name:
The one who made the call, it's likely a friend of mine.
I'll introduce you.[ST:wait ]
